<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="4"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#c0c0c0" size="6"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><br></span></font></div><div><div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><div>The health and safety of your children is our top priority. In addition to taking all necessary precautions, we aim to always keep our parents well informed of anything which comes to our attention which may affect your children.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>I am writing to inform you that there has been a confirmed case of scarlet fever in a pupil in one of our Year 2 classes. Scarlet fever is a contagious, bacterial illness that mainly affects children. It is spread by airborne droplets, through contact or from sharing towels/bed linens, etc. Symptoms initially include: a sore throat, headache, high temperature, flushed cheeks and a swollen tongue. A day or two later, the characteristic pinkish rash of scarlet fever appears which may be itchy and feel like sandpaper to touch. Please seek immediate medical advice and advise the school promptly if your child is unwell with any of the above symptoms.</div><div><br></div><div>At school, we are taking all precautions necessary including:&nbsp;</div><div><ul><li>Implementing good hygiene measures</li><li>Daily cleaning and disinfection of surfaces, door handles, stair railings, toys, bathroom accessories and food utensils</li><li>Early Yearsâ€™ toys thoroughly disinfected every Friday</li><li>Unwell children will see nurse and if necessary parents will be contacted</li><li>The children have been taught how to wash their hands by teachers and also how to cover their mouths and noses when coughing or sneezing</li></ul></div><div>If you believe your child has scarlet fever, please seek medical treatment, follow safety procedures at home and keep them away from school until they have recovered from the illness.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>For further information about scarlet fever, <a href="http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/scarlet-fever/pages/introduction.aspx">please follow this link</a></div><div><br></div><font color="#222222" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Best regards</font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br>Alison Mackey</font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Deputy Head of Primary</font></div></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><br></div></span></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font><font class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">&nbsp;</font></div>]]></td>
